tire wave]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131263286.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Inspired by India's viral Cockroach Janta Party, satirical groups like the Cockroach Awami Party and Cockroach Awami League have emerged in Pakistan. These social media-driven parties, adopting similar themes, aim to represent "lazy and unemployed" youth and Gen-Z, offering an alternative to established political factions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-gets-its-own-cockroach-awaam-party-as-indias-viral-cjp-sparks-cross-border-satire-wave/articleshow/131263286.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T17:37:54+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131263333,imgsize-1128827.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[‘It would be a big mistake’: WHO Africa chief warns against underestimating Ebola virus risk in Congo, Uganda]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264292.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[WHO's Africa director warns against underestimating the Ebola outbreak in DRC and Uganda, stressing that even one case could spread widely due to the lack of a vaccine for this strain. He urged for greater international attention, highlighting the potential risk to all from a single infected individual. Efforts are underway to boost testing and community engagement amidst challenges.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/it-would-be-a-big-mistake-who-africa-chief-warns-against-underestimating-ebola-virus-risk-in-congo-uganda/articleshow/131264292.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/it-would-be-a-big-mistake-who-africa-chief-warns-against-underestimating-ebola-virus-risk-in-congo-uganda/articleshow/131264292.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T18:52:32+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131264319,imgsize-947317.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Waiting for Green Card? Leave US first, re-enter with an immigrant visa]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264268.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/waiting-for-green-card-leave-us-first-re-enter-with-an-immigrant-visa/articleshow/131264268.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/waiting-for-green-card-leave-us-first-re-enter-with-an-immigrant-visa/articleshow/131264268.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T18:50:09+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131264282,imgsize-147244.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Drugged, raped and filmed: German woman alleges years of horrific abuse by ex-partner]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131264112.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A German woman, Claudia Wuttke, discovered videos of her former partner allegedly drugging and raping her over 16 years. Most of these alleged crimes will not face trial due to Germany's five-year statute of limitations, leaving only two cases to proceed. Wuttke expressed her distress over the majorit